item.description:
Enjoy a relaxing evening listening to young singer-songwriter Ashley Jordan. She has an incredible voice that has been described like Jewel's with a "pinch of country twang." The title song of her CD was picked up by In-Play Films in Seattle for their feature motion picture, "Good For You" set for release later this year.

Meet in the function room located in the back of the store. Come early to browse the gift shop - they have lots of great stuff. There is also a cafe so grab a beverage and bring it to the performance.

Ashley will play from 6:30 to 8:30 pm, so please arrive to take your seat by 6:15.

This is a free concert.
item.name: Early Evening Music at Tatnuck with Ashley Jordan
